{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-53-combinatoric-selections","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 53: Izbor mešavine","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Postoji samo deset načina da se izabere tri od pet, 12345:</p>\n<div style='text-align: center;'>123, 124, 125, 134, 135, 145, 234, 235, 245, i 345</div>\n<p>U kombinacijama, koristimo simbol, $\\displaystyle \\binom 5 3 = 10$</p>\n<p>Generalno, $\\displaystyle \\binom n r = \\dfrac{n!}{r!(n-r)!}$, gde je $r \\le n$, $n! = n \\times (n-1) \\times ... \\times 3 \\times 2 \\times 1$, i na $0! = 1$.</p>\n<p>Do $n = 23$, vrednost prelazi milion: $\\displaystyle \\binom {23} {10} = 1144066$.</p>\n<p>Koliko, ne mora da budu različite, vrednosti $\\displaystyle \\binom n r$ za $1 \\le n \\le 100$, koje su veće od miliona?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3a11000cf542c50feb4","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302164,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-53-combinatoric-selections"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function combinatoricSelections(limit) {\n\n  return 1;\n}\n\ncombinatoricSelections(1000000);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>combinatoricSelections(1000)</code> Trebalo bi da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof combinatoricSelections(1000) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>combinatoricSelections(1000)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 4626.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(combinatoricSelections(1000), 4626);"}